@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<main class="page-bg">
    <div class="container py-5" style="max-width:760px;">
        <a class="tb-brand" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">TutorBridge <span>Nepal</span></a>
        <h1 class="mt-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="section-sub">Last updated: July 2026</p>

        <p>TutorBridge Nepal ("we", "our", "us") connects students with verified tutors across Nepal. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and the choices you have.</p>

        <h3 class="mt-4">1. Information we collect</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Account details</strong> — your name, email address, phone number, and district when you register as a student or tutor.</li>
            <li><strong>Profile information</strong> — grade level for students; subjects, years of experience, and hourly rate for tutors.</li>
            <li><strong>Booking activity</strong> — sessions you book or teach, including dates, subjects, and status.</li>
            <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — pages you visit and searches you run on the platform, used only to improve the service.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="mt-4">2. How we use your information</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>To create and manage your account, and verify tutor credentials before their profile goes live.</li>
            <li>To match students with relevant tutors and process bookings.</li>
            <li>To send account-related notifications, such as booking confirmations.</li>
            <li>To maintain platform safety, including admin oversight of verified accounts.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="mt-4">3. How we protect your information</h3>
        <p>Passwords are never stored in plain text — they're hashed using industry-standard methods. Access to administrative tools is restricted to verified administrators and protected by two-factor authentication.</p>

        <h3 class="mt-4">4. Sharing your information</h3>
        <p>We do not sell your personal information. Your name, subjects, and public profile details are visible to other users as needed to facilitate bookings (for example, a student can see a tutor's name, subjects, and rating before booking a session). We do not share your information with third parties for advertising purposes.</p>

        <h3 class="mt-4">5. Your choices</h3>
        <p>You can update your account details at any time from your dashboard settings. If you'd like your account or data removed, contact us using the details below.</p>

        <h3 class="mt-4">6. Contact us</h3>
        <p>Questions about this policy can be sent to <a href="mailto:support@tutorbridgenepal.com">support@tutorbridgenepal.com</a>.</p>

        <a class="tb-btn-outline mt-4" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">← Back to Home</a>
    </div>
</main>